00:39:48.959 --> 00:39:52.602
Ovi dečaci nalaze se u pritvoru

552
00:39:52.728 --> 00:39:57.315
i saslušavani su u rasponu
od 14 do 30 sati.


553
00:39:57.442 --> 00:40:01.490
